msgctxt "sn56.59:0.1"
msgid "Saṃyutta Nikāya 56 "
msgstr "Linked Discourses 56 "

#. HTML: </p><p>
msgctxt "sn56.59:0.2"
msgid "6. Abhisamayavagga "
msgstr "6. Comprehension "

#. HTML: </p><h1>
msgctxt "sn56.59:0.3"
msgid "59. Paṭhamapabbatūpamasutta "
msgstr "59. A Mountain (1st) "

#. HTML: </h1></div><p>
#. REF: pts-vp-pli5.464, sc1
msgctxt "sn56.59:1.1"
msgid "“Seyyathāpi, bhikkhave, puriso himavato pabbatarājassa satta sāsapamattiyo pāsāṇasakkharā upanikkhipeyya. "
msgstr "“Mendicants, suppose a person was to place seven pebbles the size of mustard seeds on the Himalayas, the king of mountains. "

#. HTML: </p><p>
msgctxt "sn56.59:1.2"
msgid "Taṃ kiṃ maññatha, bhikkhave, "
msgstr "What do you think, mendicants? "

msgctxt "sn56.59:1.3"
msgid "katamaṃ nu kho bahutaraṃ—yā vā satta sāsapamattiyo pāsāṇasakkharā upanikkhittā, ayaṃ vā himavā pabbatarājā”ti? "
msgstr "Which is more: the seven pebbles the size of mustard seeds, or the Himalayas, the king of mountains?” "

#. HTML: </p><p>
msgctxt "sn56.59:1.4"
msgid "“Etadeva, bhante, bahutaraṃ, yadidaṃ—himavā pabbatarājā; appamattikā satta sāsapamattiyo pāsāṇasakkharā upanikkhittā. "
msgstr "“Sir, the Himalayas, the king of mountains, is certainly more. The seven pebbles the size of mustard seeds are tiny. "

msgctxt "sn56.59:1.5"
msgid "Saṅkhampi na upenti, upanidhampi na upenti, kalabhāgampi na upenti himavantaṃ pabbatarājānaṃ upanidhāya satta sāsapamattiyo pāsāṇasakkharā upanikkhittā”ti. "
msgstr "Compared to the Himalayas, they can’t be reckoned or compared, they’re not even a fraction.” "

#. HTML: </p><p>
msgctxt "sn56.59:1.6"
msgid "“Evameva kho, bhikkhave, ariyasāvakassa … pe … "
msgstr "“In the same way, for a noble disciple … "

#. HTML: </p><p>
msgctxt "sn56.59:1.7"
msgid "yogo karaṇīyo”ti. "
msgstr "That’s why you should practice meditation …” "

#. HTML: </p><p class="endsection">
msgctxt "sn56.59:1.8"
msgid "Navamaṃ. "
msgstr ""

